        <Summary>Falling blocks game</Summary>
        <Description>kblocks-kf6 is the classic falling blocks game. The idea is stack the falling blocks in a way that lines are completely filled. When a line is completed it is removed, and more space is available in the play area. When there is not enough space for blocks to fall, the game is over.</Description>
